	   <tr><td colspan=2>Off hand delay is completely independent of main hand delay. An unhasted SSoY, like any other weapon, will only swing according to its own delay in the off hand. If I remember correctly, SSoY has a delay of 24, so that's every 2.4 seconds best case (assuming the dual wield skill check is successful). If the double attack skill check also succeeds, of course, it will swing twice - but it is still independent of the main hand timer.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
